!'''Nuisance'''
|Users who have caused problems for others will have an indicator above their nameplate when the Quick Menu is open. 
Their avatar will be completely blocked, and they will be muted by default, regardless of Shield Level. However, you can still manually unmute them or show their avatar.
|-
